**Date authored:** 2026-04-17
**Scope:** validate Phases A–K of the CT/RT hard-constraint implementation.
**Authoritative sources:**
- Implementation changelog: `../planner_dev/changelog-ct-rt-hard-constraint-2026-04-17.md`
